</section>

<section class="py-5" style="background:var(--sw-white);">
    <div class="container py-lg-4">
        <div class="row g-5 align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-5 text-center px-4 order-lg-2">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604335399554-0ff2aa93de4c?w=500&h=500&fit=crop" alt="Illustration" class="img-fluid" style="border-radius:12px; box-shadow:var(--sw-shadow-lg);" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-7 pe-lg-5 order-lg-1">
                <h2 class="fw-bold mb-3 pe-lg-5" style="color:var(--sw-gray-600); font-size: 2.2rem; line-height: 1.2;">
                    How to price your laundry<br/>like we did
                </h2>
                <div style="color:var(--sw-gray-400); font-size:0.95rem; line-height:1.6;" class="mb-4 pe-lg-5">
                    <p class="mb-3">SmartWash weight guides make it extremely easy to estimate your laundry correctly without surprise charges. We believe in complete transparency and building trust with every wash.</p>
                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>T-shirt:</strong> ~0.2kg</p>
                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Jeans:</strong> ~0.7kg</p>
                    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Jacket:</strong> ~1.0kg</p>
                    <p class="mb-0"><strong>Bed Sheet:</strong> ~0.5kg</p>
                </div>
                <a href="#services" class="sw-btn sw-btn-primary px-4 py-2 mt-2">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

